metadata.title: Rōchō as the golden oni (黄金の鬼 朗澄)
metadata.name: Rōchō as the golden oni (黄金の鬼 朗澄)
metadata.description: Rōchō manifested as the golden oni (黄金の鬼の姿で現れた朗澄) (朗澄, a Japanese Buddhist monk of the Shingon sect) from "Ishiyama-dera Engi Emaki" (石山寺縁起絵巻, the illustrated handscroll of the legends of Ishiyama-dera temple).
